Make a marinade from crushed @garlic{3%gloves}, @paprika{3%tbsp}, @brown sugar{2%tbsp}, @olive oil{}, @salt, @peper, @thyme

Put marinade on @pork butt{} and let it rest in fridge ~{24%hours}

Cut @onion{3%pcs} to quarters, put them to the #baking pan{} put @thyme{} on top of onion and place @pork butt{} on top

Bake for ~{5-6%hours} at ~{140%C}